document_data.caption: A map of Tabot; the site of Mount Wiz'tcu Tan is unknown.
document_data.name: Mount Wiz'tcu Tan
document_data.mainbody: '''Mount Wiz'tcu Tan''' was a mountain in [[Tabot]].
document_data.Notable Inhabitants: It was the home of [[Ti Horr]], an old hermit and oracle, around {{YearlinkConvert|2607|SY}}.
document_data.History: At the end of his long reign, the first High Lord of Oceans [[H'Dang Li]], selected a successor and walked away into the mountains south of Mount Wiz'tcu Tan.
